26#include <sys/cdefs.h>
27__KERNEL_RCSID(0, "$NetBSD: nouveau_nvkm_subdev_fb_ramnv10.c,v 1.2 2018/08/27 04:58:33 riastradh Exp $");
28
29#include "ram.h"
30
31int
32nv10_ram_new(struct nvkm_fb *fb, struct nvkm_ram **pram)
33{
34 struct nvkm_device *device = fb->subdev.device;
35 u32 size = nvkm_rd32(device, 0x10020c) & 0xff000000;
36 u32 cfg0 = nvkm_rd32(device, 0x100200);
37 enum nvkm_ram_type type;
38
39 if (cfg0 & 0x00000001)
40 type = NVKM_RAM_TYPE_DDR1;
41 else
42 type = NVKM_RAM_TYPE_SDRAM;
43
44 return nvkm_ram_new_(&nv04_ram_func, fb, type, size, 0, pram);
45}
